_sText:
This an awp map. Players will fight in curly canals, and 45o walls. Skybox sets the environment in a favela, like my other maps (de_favela_2010).

This is beta1 version. Final version should have better detailing.

Have fun.

I appreciate your feedback.

This is a video demo that gives an idea of the gameplay of the map, particulary the interesting and unique perspectives that the S-curve canal and 45o walls create:
